The '''A4 motorway''' in [[Cyprus]] is a road which links the centre of [[Larnaca]] with the original terminal of [[Larnaca International Airport]]. Although it has an A designation, it is not a motorway, and contains all at grade separation junctions and a number of traffic lights. It follows the route of Artmedios Avenue.
